Description: 
    Implements a co-clustering model that includes spatial dendencies among 
    samples. It can be used to identify cell types and spatially variable genes
    in spatial transcriptomics studies.
Imports:
    Matrix,
    invgamma,
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.6),
    SpatialExperiment
